              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ") than the model under test. Weaker judges introduce scoring noise that degrades the reliability of the CI gate. Budget the cost: at $15/M output tokens, judging 500 cases with 200-token rationales costs ~$1.50 \u2014 trivially affordable as a CI step."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "horizontalRule"
